[*] --> Pending : Cliente crea servicio

Pending --> Assigned : Admin asigna reciclador

Assigned --> Accepted : Reciclador acepta
Assigned --> Rejected : Reciclador rechaza

Accepted --> Completed : Reciclador completa\ny sube fotos

Completed --> Rated : Cliente califica

Rated --> [*]
Rejected --> [*]

